summary: AS I WAS DRIVING DOWN THE ROAD IN MY 1999 WRANGLER, WITH ONLY 70000 MILES ON IT, AND THE ENTIRE  REAR END GAVE LOOSE. NOW I HAVE A WRANGLER, THAT IS SUPPOSEDLY WORTH 14000, THAT IS NEITHER WORTH THAT NOR IS IT DRIVABLE, AND ON TOP OF THAT I HAVE TO SHELL OUT 1000 DOLLARS IN MY OWN MONEY TO FIX THE THING.   *JB
